1
00:00:09,040 --> 00:00:09,836
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:18,808
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,850 --> 00:00:22,011
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,688 --> 00:00:26,350
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,458 --> 00:00:30,086
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,796 --> 00:00:34,890
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,399 --> 00:00:38,664
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,137 --> 00:00:44,403
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,044 --> 00:00:48,909
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,013 --> 00:00:50,742
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,815 --> 00:00:53,147
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,685 --> 00:00:56,448
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,420
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,489 --> 00:01:00,923
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,827 --> 00:01:09,391
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,368 --> 00:01:12,996
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,437 --> 00:01:16,634
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,379 --> 00:01:22,676
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,249 --> 00:01:26,773
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:30,899 --> 00:01:33,834
Inari! Give me a hand.

21
00:01:34,236 --> 00:01:35,464
I'll be right there.

22
00:01:51,820 --> 00:01:52,650
<i>This mist...</i>

23
00:01:53,522 --> 00:01:55,922
Sasuke! Sakura! They're coming!

24
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:03,261
<i>I knew he was still alive.</i>

25
00:02:04,032 --> 00:02:05,590
<i>Making an appearance so soon, eh...</i>

26
00:02:06,335 --> 00:02:07,632
Say, Kakashi Sensei.

27
00:02:07,836 --> 00:02:10,669
This is his... Hidden Mist Jutsu, right?!

28
00:02:17,612 --> 00:02:19,512
Sorry to have kept you waiting, Kakashi.

29
00:02:20,482 --> 00:02:23,212
I see you've got those brats
with you as always.

30
00:02:24,486 --> 00:02:27,853
He's still trembling. Poor thing.

31
00:02:37,933 --> 00:02:40,163
I'm trembling with... excitement.

32
00:02:42,504 --> 00:02:44,062
Do it, Sasuke.

33
00:02:56,251 --> 00:02:56,945
<i>I can see him!</i>

34
00:02:58,286 --> 00:02:59,218
Well, well.

35
00:02:59,287 --> 00:03:01,118
So you discerned
the Water Doppelganger Jutsu.

36
00:03:01,656 --> 00:03:04,147
That brat's grown quite a bit.

37
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,458
This means a rival has emerged, Haku.

38
00:03:08,130 --> 00:03:09,358
So it seems.

39
00:03:24,246 --> 00:03:25,440
Damn it!

40
00:03:30,152 --> 00:03:32,279
I'm totally late!

41
00:03:47,102 --> 00:03:52,506
Well, well... It seems my prediction
was right on the money.

42
00:03:52,941 --> 00:03:53,839
Prediction?

43
00:03:54,209 --> 00:03:55,540
That little mask...

44
00:03:56,011 --> 00:03:56,739
Oh!

45
00:03:57,179 --> 00:03:58,737
I knew it... Heh!

46
00:03:59,648 --> 00:04:01,946
So the Elite Shinobi of
the Hidden Mist thing

47
00:04:02,017 --> 00:04:04,577
was a bald faced lie!

48
00:04:05,053 --> 00:04:07,715
No matter how you look at him,
he's gotta be a comrade of Zabuza.

49
00:04:08,323 --> 00:04:09,984
Standing together with him and all...

50
00:04:11,126 --> 00:04:14,061
How dare he show up like that
after what he did!

51
00:04:14,596 --> 00:04:17,565
I hate brats who think they're so cool...

52
00:04:17,766 --> 00:04:19,199
He's better than you, Kakashi Sensei.

53
00:04:19,468 --> 00:04:20,935
Oh... really?

54
00:04:21,837 --> 00:04:23,702
I'll do it.

55
00:04:24,039 --> 00:04:24,562
Huh?

56
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:30,043
With his bad acting...
I hate brats who think they're so cool!

57
00:04:30,545 --> 00:04:32,342
Sasuke, you are <i>so</i> cool!

58
00:04:33,815 --> 00:04:37,615
<i>That Sakura doesn't take stabs at Sasuke...</i>

59
00:04:39,154 --> 00:04:40,815
He's an impressive youth.

60
00:04:41,423 --> 00:04:42,082
Hmm...

61
00:04:42,591 --> 00:04:44,354
Even though those Water Clones

62
00:04:44,426 --> 00:04:48,123
have only 1/10th the strength
of their original...

63
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:50,520
To think he went that well.

64
00:04:51,766 --> 00:04:53,791
However, you made
the preemptive move.

65
00:04:54,603 --> 00:04:55,365
Go!

66
00:04:56,271 --> 00:04:56,828
Right!

67
00:05:00,675 --> 00:05:01,266
What?!

68
00:05:11,486 --> 00:05:17,322
<i>Haku's Secret Jutsu.</i>
<i>Crystal Ice Mirrors</i>

69
00:05:28,537 --> 00:05:30,437
Are you Tazuna's daughter?

70
00:05:30,805 --> 00:05:33,330
Sorry, but you're coming with us.

71
00:05:47,389 --> 00:05:48,185
Mom!

72
00:05:49,424 --> 00:05:51,824
Don't come out!
Get out of here, quick!

73
00:05:52,627 --> 00:05:53,651
What's with you, brat?!

74
00:05:55,797 --> 00:05:57,662
Shall we take him, too?

75
00:05:58,233 --> 00:06:00,258
One hostage is fine.

76
00:06:01,736 --> 00:06:02,668
<i>Hostage...?!</i>

77
00:06:04,072 --> 00:06:04,902
Then...

78
00:06:06,808 --> 00:06:08,173
Shall we kill him?

79
00:06:12,914 --> 00:06:13,710
Wait!

80
00:06:20,088 --> 00:06:21,487
If you lay a hand on that child...

81
00:06:22,090 --> 00:06:23,614
I'll bite off my tongue
and kill myself!

82
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:31,196
You want a hostage, right?

83
00:06:39,374 --> 00:06:42,502
Thank your mom, kid.

84
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:52,013
Oh, man...
It's not enough...

85
00:06:52,087 --> 00:06:55,579
Knock it off.
You just tried out your sword earlier.

86
00:06:56,124 --> 00:06:58,251
Forget it already and
let's take the woman.

87
00:07:06,935 --> 00:07:08,562
Mom, I'm sorry...

88
00:07:09,604 --> 00:07:10,400
I'm so sorry!

89
00:07:13,742 --> 00:07:17,234
I'm weak, so I can't protect you...

90
00:07:25,253 --> 00:07:29,280
I don't want to die...
I'm scared!

91
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:32,820
<i>You crybaby...</i>

92
00:07:34,863 --> 00:07:37,889
<i>So you're just gonna cry all day</i>
<i>like the lead in a tragedy?</i>

93
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:43,069
<i>An idiot like you can just</i>
<i>cry forever! You crybaby!</i>

94
00:07:44,606 --> 00:07:47,541
<i>He's probably tired of crying.</i>

95
00:07:48,943 --> 00:07:52,310
<i>So, he knows the true meaning of</i>
<i>the word strong.</i>

96
00:07:53,648 --> 00:07:55,912
<i>Like your father.</i>

97
00:08:02,090 --> 00:08:03,990
<i>For the things I truly hold</i>
<i>dear to myself...</i>

98
00:08:04,059 --> 00:08:08,393
<i>I protect them until the end</i>
<i>with both these arms,</i>

99
00:08:08,463 --> 00:08:09,896
<i>even if it looks like I might lose my life!</i>

100
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,402
<i>Inari...</i>

101
00:08:26,581 --> 00:08:27,775
Can I...

102
00:08:29,751 --> 00:08:31,776
can I also become strong...?

103
00:08:37,525 --> 00:08:38,492
Dad!

104
00:08:42,831 --> 00:08:47,063
Looking at that beautiful skin
of yours makes me want to cut you.

105
00:08:47,702 --> 00:08:49,067
Hey... walk faster.

106
00:08:49,471 --> 00:08:50,460
Wait!

107
00:08:54,175 --> 00:08:54,732
Inari!

108
00:08:55,477 --> 00:08:58,139
What? It's just the kid from before.

109
00:08:59,647 --> 00:09:03,913
Get... get away from my mom!

110
00:09:04,619 --> 00:09:07,782
Man... This brat's hopeless.

111
00:09:08,523 --> 00:09:09,217
Let's do it!

112
00:09:12,761 --> 00:09:14,285
If you do that, I'll bite off
my tongue and

113
00:09:16,297 --> 00:09:17,889
Shut up. Go to sleep.

114
00:09:18,533 --> 00:09:19,727
I... na... ri.

115
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:35,044
<i>Well, well...</i>
<i>He can see that speed, eh...</i>

116
00:09:37,051 --> 00:09:37,642
<i>Yes...</i>

117
00:09:38,319 --> 00:09:41,311
Sakura, surround Tazuna and
don't move away from me.

118
00:09:42,157 --> 00:09:43,590
Let Sasuke handle him!

119
00:09:43,792 --> 00:09:44,281
Okay.

120
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:54,725
I don't want to have to kill you...

121
00:09:55,503 --> 00:09:57,994
I'd like for you to back down.

122
00:09:59,107 --> 00:10:00,199
Nonsense...

123
00:10:01,209 --> 00:10:02,073
I knew it...

124
00:10:03,711 --> 00:10:07,977
But you won't be able to keep up
with my speed.

125
00:10:08,683 --> 00:10:12,449
Also, I've already made
two preemptive moves.

126
00:10:12,787 --> 00:10:14,015
Two preemptive moves?

127
00:10:14,522 --> 00:10:17,320
The first one is the scattered water.

128
00:10:18,259 --> 00:10:22,161
And the second one was
blocking one of your hands...

129
00:10:22,897 --> 00:10:27,357
Therefore, you'll just be able
to defend my attack...

130
00:10:29,771 --> 00:10:31,864
<i>What?! With one hand he's...?!</i>

131
00:10:34,943 --> 00:10:36,706
<i>A one handed Sign?</i>

132
00:10:37,645 --> 00:10:39,169
<i>I've never seen such a thing before...</i>

133
00:10:41,983 --> 00:10:44,577
A Thousand Needles of Death!

134
00:10:49,891 --> 00:10:52,155
So he doesn't want to kill him... eh.

135
00:10:53,361 --> 00:10:54,760
I wonder if that's how he really feels...

136
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:56,858
Sasuke!

137
00:11:01,269 --> 00:11:03,863
<i>Remember...that training...</i>

138
00:11:12,614 --> 00:11:14,411
<i>Build up Chakra at one burst...</i>

139
00:11:32,533 --> 00:11:33,693
The Substitution Jutsu...?!

140
00:11:34,168 --> 00:11:35,533
The woman... Hmm?

141
00:11:35,770 --> 00:11:37,761
Sorry I was late.

142
00:11:42,010 --> 00:11:45,605
Heroes usually appear
on the scene late, so...

143
00:11:46,748 --> 00:11:47,840
Naruto!

144
00:11:50,718 --> 00:11:53,278
Inari, you did well!

145
00:11:53,488 --> 00:11:54,147
Huh?

146
00:11:54,489 --> 00:11:59,222
Thanks to you distracting them,
I was able to save your mom.

147
00:12:05,733 --> 00:12:09,169
Naruto... how did you know that
those samurai were here?

148
00:12:11,172 --> 00:12:14,403
In the forest, there was a boar that
had been cut up with a sword.

149
00:12:14,943 --> 00:12:19,209
Other than that,
there were trees with lots of cuts.

150
00:12:19,814 --> 00:12:22,442
They headed in
the direction of your house...

151
00:12:22,684 --> 00:12:24,117
so I got worried.

152
00:12:25,753 --> 00:12:27,015
I see.

153
00:12:27,488 --> 00:12:28,512
Well...

154
00:12:28,923 --> 00:12:31,824
If it isn't the no good Ninja
that Tazuna hired...

155
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,156
Let's do it...

156
00:12:33,361 --> 00:12:33,986
Yeah...

157
00:12:34,996 --> 00:12:35,587
Here they come!

158
00:12:41,869 --> 00:12:43,734
Hah! Something like that won't work!

159
00:12:46,774 --> 00:12:47,706
Fools.

160
00:12:48,242 --> 00:12:50,335
Prepare yourself!

161
00:13:05,512 --> 00:13:07,207
W-Wow...!

162
00:13:09,883 --> 00:13:11,373
It's done!

163
00:13:14,087 --> 00:13:17,420
Naruto, you're just like... a Ninja!

164
00:13:17,524 --> 00:13:21,585
You fool.
I was a Ninja to start with!

165
00:13:31,972 --> 00:13:33,906
<i>Build up Chakra at one burst...</i>

166
00:13:35,876 --> 00:13:36,535
to <i>the feet!</i>

167
00:13:45,752 --> 00:13:46,650
He vanished...

168
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,120
You're surprisingly stupid...

169
00:13:59,099 --> 00:14:03,536
From here on...
you'll only defend my attack!

170
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,720
To think Haku would
lose in speed...

171
00:14:24,925 --> 00:14:28,861
It seems that I'm faster than you...

172
00:14:30,263 --> 00:14:34,927
I can't have you mocking our team,
calling them brats...

173
00:14:36,403 --> 00:14:37,461
He may not look it,

174
00:14:37,537 --> 00:14:40,631
but Sasuke is the number one rookie
of the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

175
00:14:42,008 --> 00:14:44,909
And Sakura is our sharpest...

176
00:14:47,013 --> 00:14:49,345
Hah! Serves you right!

177
00:14:51,785 --> 00:14:55,482
And the other one is
the number one hyperactive,

178
00:14:55,555 --> 00:14:59,787
knucklehead Ninja, Naruto Uzumaki.

179
00:15:04,131 --> 00:15:05,098
You have a cold?

180
00:15:05,165 --> 00:15:06,723
I'm okay.

181
00:15:07,601 --> 00:15:12,038
Anyway...
Sorry about yesterday, Inari.

182
00:15:12,506 --> 00:15:13,234
Huh?

183
00:15:15,609 --> 00:15:20,569
Branding you a crybaby...
Forget I ever said that.

184
00:15:23,984 --> 00:15:25,713
You're strong!

185
00:15:34,594 --> 00:15:35,424
Dang it!

186
00:15:35,862 --> 00:15:38,922
I... decided never
to cry again, but...

187
00:15:41,968 --> 00:15:49,602
Now you'll laugh at me again
and call me a crybaby.

188
00:15:51,478 --> 00:15:52,410
What're you saying...?!

189
00:15:55,515 --> 00:15:58,416
It's okay... when you're happy.

190
00:16:04,624 --> 00:16:08,492
It's okay to cry when you're happy!

191
00:16:10,664 --> 00:16:11,688
Naruto...

192
00:16:21,374 --> 00:16:25,208
Now then.
I can leave the rest to you, right?

193
00:16:25,679 --> 00:16:26,304
Yeah...

194
00:16:27,447 --> 00:16:30,075
Okay, I'm going to hop over
to the bridge for a bit.

195
00:16:32,118 --> 00:16:37,249
Man, it's tough being a hero!
That's for sure!

196
00:16:49,636 --> 00:16:51,331
Haku, do you know what this means?

197
00:16:51,538 --> 00:16:53,563
At this rate, you'll be defeated
by your intended victim...

198
00:16:54,341 --> 00:16:55,103
Yes...

199
00:16:59,412 --> 00:17:00,174
What...?

200
00:17:05,385 --> 00:17:06,443
It's unfortunate...

201
00:17:08,255 --> 00:17:10,246
Is this... cold air...?

202
00:17:23,236 --> 00:17:24,100
Hidden Jutsu!

203
00:17:42,489 --> 00:17:44,081
Crystal Ice Mirrors!

204
00:17:52,899 --> 00:17:54,867
What is it? What's that Jutsu?

205
00:18:15,322 --> 00:18:17,415
Are these... mirrors?!

206
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:19,425
What...

207
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:20,824
in the world...?!

208
00:18:23,596 --> 00:18:24,358
Damn it!

209
00:18:28,902 --> 00:18:32,235
I'm your opponent, aren't I?

210
00:18:33,273 --> 00:18:37,539
Since that Jutsu has appeared...
he's done for.

211
00:18:41,481 --> 00:18:43,847
Now then... I'll start.

212
00:18:44,784 --> 00:18:49,221
I shall show you...
my true speed!

213
00:18:53,693 --> 00:18:54,387
Sasuke!

214
00:19:01,267 --> 00:19:02,029
Sasuke!

215
00:19:22,389 --> 00:19:26,018
If you make a move,
I'll kill those two!!

216
00:19:36,136 --> 00:19:37,364
I'm sorry, Tazuna!

217
00:19:38,304 --> 00:19:40,534
I'm stepping away from here for a bit.

218
00:19:42,409 --> 00:19:44,377
Sure. Go!

219
00:19:48,214 --> 00:19:48,942
Sakura!

220
00:19:49,949 --> 00:19:50,813
Sasuke!

221
00:19:53,586 --> 00:19:54,985
Take this!

222
00:20:13,706 --> 00:20:14,900
He caught it?!

223
00:20:30,924 --> 00:20:31,447
What?!

224
00:20:40,733 --> 00:20:41,222
Who is it?!

225
00:20:44,804 --> 00:20:48,331
<i>It's that idiot...that showoff...</i>

226
00:20:50,210 --> 00:20:54,738
The number one hyperactive,
knucklehead Ninja...

227
00:21:09,131 --> 00:21:10,530
Naruto Uzumaki...

228
00:21:11,133 --> 00:21:13,624
is finally here!

229
00:22:52,601 --> 00:22:54,398
Naruto Uzumaki is finally here!

230
00:22:54,536 --> 00:22:55,662
It'll be okay.

231
00:22:55,737 --> 00:22:57,932
Now that the hero of the story
has appeared,

232
00:22:58,006 --> 00:23:01,100
I'll smash those stupid
funny looking mirrors in no time...

233
00:23:01,176 --> 00:23:04,270
Huh? Why won't mirrors
made of ice break?

234
00:23:04,479 --> 00:23:05,969
Why won't they melt?

235
00:23:06,348 --> 00:23:09,749
What the heck is going on here?!

236
00:23:10,752 --> 00:23:13,880
Next episode:
"The Number One Hyperactive
Knucklehead Ninja Joins the Fight!"

237
00:23:13,989 --> 00:23:16,856
As for me, will I be able
to kick butt once again?
